{
  "stem": "22979.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many, I don't know, momentarily, all of the names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the whole complex-- I don't know, at peacetime in January, 1945, how many thousands, and now hundreds of thousands prisoners.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Snow was about over a meter or two meters high.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had to march to the mountains, Carpathian mountains, not where the civilian population was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The first who marched, they paved the road for the rest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The SS was on the sides, with the ox [? leg ?] usually.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some of horses were too-- on horses, I would say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But when we left, we who were in the special kommando, we were well fed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we put on clothing, because we could still grab for pants, and underwear, and warm things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But those from the camp had only those very thin summery clothing, wooden clogs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had already shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And each shoe was different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It doesn't matter, but they were shoes and warm socks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And when we walked, you know, who was not able to walk was shot right away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We walked way behind our kommando in the back of the long lines of prisoners, so we walked over corpses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If the corpse has still something usable, a shoe or a sweater, we took it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But we didn't have strength to pull them up to the side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So, you know, it was stepped in in the snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The road were paved with corpses, but we walked about a week towards Berlin, because the part around Berlin, they needed still us to clean the airfields, to clean, you know, the bombarded cities.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The only thing but we had to eat was snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Frozen, wet, slept-- you know, came, came the night, we slept on the snow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, you get wet, you huddle.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
